{
  "stem": "18670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the same street we had a Jewish man living with a Christian woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a divorcee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on Tuesdays, the dentist, the single dentist, single man who was a dentist, used to drive in from Vienna, had a practice there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would leave Thursday afternoon and go back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me-- yes and no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew they were anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like this teacher, we knew that he belonged to the [GERMAN], the [GERMAN] group there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew that he was a Fascist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew about others that were hiding it, but you could tell after a while, after the Nazi party had been outlawed, who the Nazis were.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But our experience with the customers, we were not in the main-- where the store was, it was not in the main place, plaza, it's-- where the other stores were.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was on a side street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the customers that came to us, very friendly business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father ran a credit business and never charged any interest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the people used to buy merchandise would by Christmas time-- the big shopping was twice a year, Christmas time, then they'll pay at Easter for the merchandise they bought at Christmas.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They buy Easter merchandise, clothing, and they'll pay at Christmas time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or they pay it in installments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After all-- after a while, this became the Depression years, 1930s and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the whole, we didn't have any problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even after the Nazis came-- well, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came in and it became critical, because they posted a Nazi stormtrooper in front of it and-- while I was in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
